comment: Gordon (NOP) and Tucker (PHO) make incidental contact with one another during rebounding.
An inadvertent whistle was blown following the rebound by New Orleans. The ball was inbounded at the point of interruption.
Davis (NOP) sets the screen on Tucker (PHO) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Anderson (NOP) splits his feet on the perimeter at the start of his drive.
Anderson (NOP) sets the screen on Knight (PHO) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Cunningham (NOP) maintains legal guarding position as he defends Bledsoe's (PHO) driving layup attempt.
Leuer (PHO) legally contests Holiday's (NOP) driving layup attempt.
Morris (PHO) makes incidental contact with Davis (NOP) as he attempts to defend his layup attempt.
Gee (NOP) makes incidental contact with Bledsoe (PHO) as he starts his drive to the basket.
Davis (NOP) obtains a legal guarding position, and Bledsoe (PHO) jumps backwards and intiates the contact with Davis.
Morris (PHO) dislodges Davis (NOP), affecting his ability to retrieve the rebound.
Holiday (NOP) makes incidental contact with Knight (PHO) as he creates space to catch the inbound pass.
Tucker (PHO) commits a take foul on Holiday (NOP).
Smith (NOP) grabs Knight (PHO) and affects his ability to retrieve the loose ball.
Price (PHO) commits a take foul on Holiday (NOP).
Holiday (NOP) makes incidental "high-five" contact with Leuer (PHO) after the shot has been released.
Booker (PHO) commits a take foul on Gordon (NOP).
